---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions — YT Downloader" description="Terms and conditions for using YT Downloader services.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-24 w-full">
    <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:text-body prose-headings:text-ink max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-1.28px] mb-8">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">By accessing and using YT Downloader, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use our service.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Use of Service</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">YT Downloader provides a tool to download media from publicly available URLs. You agree to use this service only for lawful purposes. You are strictly prohibited from:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
