        <li>Using the service for commercial distribution of downloaded content.</li>
        <li>Attempting to bypass our rate limits or security measures.</li>
        <li>Using automated scripts or bots to access our API without explicit permission.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Copyright & Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">YT Downloader respects the intellectual property rights of others. We do not host, store, or distribute any copyrighted material on our servers. Our tool acts only as a proxy to fetch publicly available data requested directly by the user. The user assumes all legal responsibility for the media they choose to download and how they choose to use it.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">The service is provided "as is" and "as available" without any warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the service will be uninterrupted, secure, or error-free. We are not responsible for the quality, accuracy, or legality of the content downloaded through our service.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">In no event shall YT Downloader, its developers, or affiliates be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential or punitive damages arising out of or relating to your use of the service.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Your continued use of the service following any such modification constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
